example.p:
We must find coefficients a,b,c,d such that

  \begin{bmatrix}1\amp 3\\-1\amp 2\end{bmatrix}
  =
  a\begin{bmatrix}1\amp 0\\0\amp 1\end{bmatrix}
  +b\begin{bmatrix}1\amp 0\\0\amp -1\end{bmatrix}
  +c\begin{bmatrix}0\amp 1\\1\amp 0\end{bmatrix}
  +d\begin{bmatrix}0\amp -1\\1\amp 0\end{bmatrix},

or equivalently,

  \begin{bmatrix}1\amp 3\\-1\amp 2\end{bmatrix}
  =
  \begin{bmatrix}
    a+b \amp c-d \\
    c+d \amp a-b
  \end{bmatrix}.
